examples.en: Actors always look for meaty roles.

She has long since moved on from the roles of her youth.
She was famous as an interpreter of Shakespearean roles.
She is known in Italy for a number of minor roles in films.
In a reversal of roles, he is now taking care of his mother.
They played up the silliness of their roles for camp effect.
My mother and I reversed our roles. Now I'm taking care of her.
She's a marvelous actress who submerges herself totally in her roles.

We'll switch roles this time, and you can wash the dishes while I dry them.
